{
  "number": 330,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/330",
  "title": "Silence React dev warnings",
  "body": "After started using v0.5.0, I'm getting a console log with  \"Download the React DevTools for a better development experience: https://fb.me/react-devtools\", which is a bit annoying.\n\nIt seems like `browserify`ing with `NODE_ENV=production` makes these warning messages disappear (See https://github.com/facebook/react/issues/3877 ).\n\nCould we do that for our releases?\n",
